descriptionHtml:
[i]This is a preset I made by request, it contains two presets for racemenu.
I tried my best to make her look like the picture, sorry if ya think I failed tell me if i did, and yes yes I made her from my current character, that doesn’t mean it was easy!
I used my character because she looks almost like her already, check my images to see my character.
The second preset was an idea for a follower, a dremora follower called tajea.
If you have RaceMenuMorphsCBBE you will get her shape too. just drop the presets in Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen and go ingame and load it from the preset tab, though everyone knows that but you know those ones that dont ;)
Things ya need
YMMP make up  [url=http://yev.restrictedareagaming.net/yevmods]Here[/url] Updated :)
The eyes of amber  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/?]Here[/url]
SG hairs hdt     [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]Here[/url]
True brows      [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50307/?]Here[/url]
TheCoenaculiCBBE [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35677/?]Here[/url]
Glowing_Eyes  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/21232/?]Here[/url] if your planning on using the dremora preset
KJ Tattoos   [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?]Here[/url]
SGEyebrows  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]Here[/url]
EmpyreanWarpaints  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61332/?]Here.[/url]
Your life  google it :)
Please endorse these mods if you use them

If you don’t have any of the tattoo mods you will get a purple\weird looking body part where that tattoo is missing so just go in the body paint section and set the missing ones to default or your own tattoo.
Same with the hair YOU 0_0 will have no hair when you load the preset.
If you cant bother to download anything else and just want a normal preset then download the vanilla preset.
                                                                                                          ___
Sorry if you think my mod sucks, im just giving back to the community (-_-)
                                                                        

[/i]
